HEADWORD: Semiparabola
<hw>Sem`i*pa*rab"o*la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Geom.)</fld> <def>One branch of a parabola, being terminated at
the principal vertex of the curve.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

